br.com.henriquewilhelm.orbit

Class Event

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.henriquewilhelm.orbit.Event
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MoonEvent

    public class Event
extends java.lang.Object
    The Event class gathers the calculations of one element of the solar system (Sun, Mercury, Venus, Earth, Mars, Jupiter, Saturn, Uranus, Neptune, Pluto) The calculations are:

    Rise and set Time HorizonToHorizonCrossing type Time meridianCrossing (noon) Time, antimeridianCrossing (Midnigth) position (rightAscention, declination, longitudeEcliptic and distance)

    Version:
    v2.0.0
    Author:
    Henrique Wilhelm v1.0.0, zoglmannk v1.0.0
